<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q1_v10" title="Q1_v10" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En la pizarra aparece la siguiente operación:</p>
    <p>
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
    </p>
    <p>¿Cuál es su valor?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Selecciona una alternativa.</qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">−36<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Primero, dentro del segundo paréntesis se obtiene −4 − 3 = −7. Luego, (−5)(−7) = 35, porque el producto de dos números negativos es positivo. Finalmente, 35 − 1 = 34. Por lo tanto, el valor de la operación no es −36.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">34<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Se calcula primero el paréntesis: −4 − 3 = −7. Después, (−5)(−7) = 35. Finalmente, 35 − 1 = 34. Por eso, el valor de la operación es 34.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">36<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Primero, −4 − 3 = −7. Luego, (−5)(−7) = 35. Después todavía hay que restar 1: 35 − 1 = 34. Por lo tanto, el valor de la operación no es 36.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">4<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al calcular el segundo paréntesis, −4 − 3 = −7. Luego, (−5)(−7) = 35. Finalmente, 35 − 1 = 34. Por lo tanto, el valor de la operación no es 4.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Resolver el segundo paréntesis</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces la operación queda:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Multiplicar los dos números entre paréntesis</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>35</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Esto ocurre porque el producto de dos números negativos es positivo.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Restar 1 al resultado obtenido</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>35</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>34</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El valor de la operación es 34, por lo tanto la alternativa correcta es la B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>